name: Overall Performance
query: SELECT participants.purple_agent AS id, ROUND(r.average_alpha_score, 0) AS "Alpha Score", r.num_tasks AS "Tasks", r.num_successful AS "Passed" FROM (SELECT participants, results[1] AS r FROM results) ORDER BY r.average_alpha_score DESC

name: Detailed Results
query: SELECT participants.purple_agent AS id, r.ticker AS "Ticker", r.version AS "Version", ROUND(r.average_alpha_score, 0) AS "Alpha Score" FROM (SELECT participants, results[1] AS r FROM results) ORDER BY r.average_alpha_score DESC
